#

Savory Mushroom Barley Soup

60 min
$10.5
220 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh FiberLow Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEasyHearty

Description

A hearty and flavorful mushroom barley soup, perfect for a comforting meal any day of the week.

Ingredients

  • barley: 1 cup
  • mushrooms (sliced): 2 cups
  • carrots (diced): 1 cup
  • celery (diced): 1 cup
  • onion (chopped): 1 medium
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • garlic (minced): 3 cloves
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh parsley (chopped): 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • thyme (dried): 1 teaspoon
  • bay leaf: 1
